3	97	681	681	he	5	1,"Long , long ago there lived an old man and his wife who supported themselves by cultivating a small plot of land . Their life had been a very happy and peaceful one save for one great sorrow . This was they had no child . Their only pet was a dog named Shiro . On him they lavished all the affection of their old age . Indeed , they loved him so much that whenever they had anything nice to eat they denied themselves to give it to Shiro . Now Shiro means "
